properties.querySQL:
select a.usercode,DATE_FORMAT(a.attdate,'%Y-%m-%d') attdate,a.username,a.unitcode,
case when  beginTime<=DATE_FORMAT(attdate,'%Y-%m-%d %08:%45:%00') then b.leaveType else a.onduty_type end onLeave,
case when  beginTime<=DATE_FORMAT(attdate,'%Y-%m-%d %08:%45:%00') then b.leaveCity else '' end oncity,
case when  endtime>=DATE_FORMAT(attdate,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') then b.leaveType else a.offduty_type end offLeave,
case when  endtime>=DATE_FORMAT(attdate,'%Y-%m-%d %15:%30:%00') then b.leaveCity else '' end offcity
from (
	SELECT * FROM v_attendance_daily where  attdate between :begindate and :enddate 
)a left join (select * from leaveinfo where flowresult in('通过','审批中')) b on a.usercode=b.usercode and DATE_FORMAT(a.attdate,'%Y-%m-%d') between DATE_FORMAT(b.beginTime,'%Y-%m-%d') and DATE_FORMAT(b.endTime,'%Y-%m-%d')
where 1=1 [:unitcode | and a.unitcode=:unitcode] [:(splitforin)usercode | and a.usercode in (:usercode)]
